re_item_assets/steam/apps/2009500/extras/e3e6ad17b70e538c0dd65e248412e293.poster.avif?t=1711386058\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2009500/extras/e3e6ad17b70e538c0dd65e248412e293.webm?t=1711386058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2009500/extras/e3e6ad17b70e538c0dd65e248412e293.mp4?t=1711386058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNCOVER A DARK PAST</h2>Follow Gregory's journey to escape this magical loop. But in order to escape, he must confront his dark past.<br><br>",
